{"tid":1332624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事］岩岩經過藥房買野","createTime":"2019-07-19T11:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T11:23:43.000Z","uid":282280,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6c8110544f08dae84d23deb551baff51c1cf34","tid":1332624,"uid":282280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"見到兩個老人家買紙巾、口罩、保鮮紙（三大袋），同個藥房老闆傾計...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藥房老闆：人人都有自由既，希望佢地成功啦！<br />\n<br />\n老人家：係呀，咁我地都支持佢地，但我地淨係可以為佢地做呢d...我地一把年紀走唔切架，叫我地衝就唔得架啦，除左做下呢d幫佢地架咋～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係隔離聽到起雞皮，<br />\n其實你地幫左我地好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少令大家知道我地背後仲有一班咁有愛既長輩支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地既綿力同心意！激勵左好多年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b7100866d990f5f17bf20a2bd01052b7fc32e52c","tid":1332624,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"到時見"},{"pid":"9fc305a8d34d55ab5f0a73f3a4d868ef1ae87718","tid":1332624,"uid":181813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca9ef82260ac483d8e18b45ea3321cd54b82cc9","tid":1332624,"uid":154631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"46歲被告黃堅海任職的士司機，到觀塘裁判法院應訊"},{"pid":"a778780e8197d1490f5d02bc0c7966d7ccc7443b","tid":1332624,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"